    <h2 class="font-bold text-center text-xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-violet-400 mt-32 mb-8">Cognitive</h2>

    <p class="text-lg/loose md:text-xl/loose lg:text-2xl/loose max-w-prose mb-8">Cognitive disabilities arise as a result of conditions that a person has from birth. They can result from injury, infection, chemical imbalances, or other conditions a person develops later in life. Theres no one way to describe cognitive disabilities, as they can affect one or more mental functions by different degrees. Some examples of Cognitive Disabilities are:</p>

    <ul class="list-disc text-lg/loose md:text-xl/loose lg:text-2xl/loose max-w-prose mb-8 ml-8">
        <li class="mb-4">Non-Verbal Learning Disability</li>
        <li class="mb-4">Autism</li>
        <li class="mb-4">ADHD</li>
    </ul>

