    <h2 class="font-bold text-center text-xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-violet-400 mt-32 mb-8">Dyslexia</h2>

    <p class="text-lg/loose md:text-xl/loose lg:text-2xl/loose max-w-prose mb-8">People with dyslexia have  high levels of cognitive functioning, but difficulty with reading words. Many describe their experience of reading as letters moving around, swapping in and out of place.</p>

    <h3 class="text-center text-xl md:text-xl lg:text-3xl text-violet-400 mt-8 mb-8">Challenges & Solutions for People with Dyslexia</h3>

    <table class="text-lg/loose md:text-xl/loose lg:text-2xl/loose">
        <caption class="text-[#16b6ff] bg-[#141f39] rounded-lg mb-4">Digital Environments</caption>
