        <tbody>
            
            <tr class="border-b">
                <td class="border-r w-1/2 p-8">Difficulty understanding content as it's presented</td>
                <td class="p-8">Allow people to apply a custom style sheet</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
                <td class="border-r w-1/2 p-8">Difficulty solving CAPTCHA</td>
                <td class="p-8">Allow people to change the type of security check presented</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
                <td class="border-r w-1/2 p-8">Difficulty spelling words correctly</td>
                <td class="p-8">Spelling or grammar checkers</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
                <td class="border-r w-1/2 p-8">Difficulty processing visual content</td>
                <td class="p-8">
                    <ul class="list-disc ml-8">
                        <li>Screen readers</li>
                        <li>Additional time to complete tasks</li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
                <td class="border-r w-1/2 p-8">Require additional time to read and process content</td>
                <td class="p-8">
                    <ul class="list-disc ml-8">
                        <li>Extended time-outs</li>
                        <li>Screen readers to get text in an auditory mode to reinforce what is being seen</li>
                        <li>Screen readers that highlight words</li>
                        <li>Enhancing visible focus</li>
                        <li>Allow ample time to complete tasks</li>
                        <li>Use special programs that present words with pictures</li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
                <td class="border-r w-1/2 p-8">Often see p, b, d, q as the same letter</td>
                <td class="p-8">Allow people to customize fonts, contrast, or add underlines</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
                <td class="border-r w-1/2 p-8">Often see words as floating</td>
                <td class="p-8">Use the font developed for Dyslexia</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
